extends layout 
block content 
    section.about-us
        div.container
          div.row
            div.col-md-6
              h3 About Us
              p We at Edumate believe that education is a lifetime adventure, and we are here to assist students of all ages and backgrounds in achieving success. Our platform offers a complete set of educational materials and tools that are intended to empower both learners and instructors.
              p We have you covered if you want to enhance your grades, gain new skills, or explore new subjects. Our expert and educator team has created a wide selection of courses and learning resources, including interactive quizzes and videos, as well as in-depth guides and tutorials.
              p However, Edumate is more than simply a learning platform. We are a community of learners and instructors united by a desire for knowledge and personal development. Our objective is to foster a welcome and encouraging atmosphere in which students may interact with one another and with their professors, exchange ideas and insights, and find inspiration and motivation to achieve their goals.
              p 
            div.col-md-6
              img(src='images/aboutus.jpg', alt='Image of our team', style="height: 590px; width: 400px;")